2026-06-12T09:44:33.461997Z  INFO http.request{method=POST path=/api/v1/erp/init/initialize-with-db trace_id=6aa87b42453d4695aa8ca46256e39925 span_id=6b6f373271fe0acf parent_span_id="" sampled=true}: sqlx::query: summary="INSERT INTO \"seaql_migrations\" (\"version\", …" db.statement="\n\nINSERT INTO \"seaql_migrations\" (\"version\", \"applied_at\") VALUES ($1, $2) RETURNING \"version\"\n" rows_affected=1 rows_returned=1 elapsed=55.507714ms elapsed_secs=0.055507714
